1. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Food          | pear     | raspberry |
| Hobby         | camping  | dancing   |
| Cigar   | cain | blend       |
| Pet           | hedgehog | ferret    |

