.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, october
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
1. the australian is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
2. the nurse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Birthday          | october         | september    |
| Job           | entrepreneur | nurse   |
| Nationality   | australian   | thai    |
| Transport     | boat         | scooter |

 